  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware The Willow Man as he lurks throughout the halls, in your dreams, and into your soul. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334060/extras/bathTub1.gif?t=1745956011\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Willow Man is a survival horror game where you take on the shoes of Rin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rin and her friends decide one day to explore a house on the hill. Rumours have spread</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >about that place. Some say evil dwells there. Unfazed by this they enter and</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >what awaits them is not what they expected. Survive, hide, find a way out before</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Willow Man finds you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334060/extras/RunGif1.gif?t=1745956011\" /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frantic Chases</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sanity Meter</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Fights</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Endings</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive, Fight, or Hide to survive the night</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original Art brimming with personality</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334060/extras/CharactersForDescriptionArt.png?t=1745956011\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334060/extras/cee3ecc423ad3644f8a3c6bec3844b6c.poster.avif?t=1745956011\" width=638 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334060/extras/cee3ecc423ad3644f8a3c6bec3844b6c.webm?t=1745956011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334060/extras/cee3ecc423ad3644f8a3c6bec3844b6c.mp4?t=1745956011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware The Willow Man as he lurks throughout the halls, in your dreams, and into your soul. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334060/extras/bathTub1.gif?t=1745956011\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Willow Man is a survival horror game where you take on the shoes of Rin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rin and her friends decide one day to explore a house on the hill. Rumours have spread</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >about that place. Some say evil dwells there. Unfazed by this they enter and</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >what awaits them is not what they expected. Survive, hide, find a way out before</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Willow Man finds you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334060/extras/RunGif1.gif?t=1745956011\" /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frantic Chases</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sanity Meter</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Fights</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Endings</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive, Fight, or Hide to survive the night</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original Art brimming with personality</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334060/extras/CharactersForDescriptionArt.png?t=1745956011\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn